    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>An unstandardized name for whitish pigment made from bismuth nitrate,  bismuth oxychloride, or from a calcium carbonate powder obtained from pulverizing and calcining mother-of-pearl.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
